{"tid":1043246,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[小桃園食飯又唔算數?]劉炳章斥學生圍堵教授涉禁錮：似黑社會刮友","createTime":"2019-03-02T06:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T17:00:08.000Z","uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2b1f20f83b7e565874c671182997cbcd6ce62771","tid":1043246,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:15:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190302/59321570\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59321570&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=92481fc2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190302%2F59321570&h=f551089b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190302/59321570</a><br />\n<br />\n理大重罰去年因民主牆管理問題與校方管理層發生衝突的4名學生，分別判處停學、社會服務令及即時踢出校。校董劉炳章今早前往北京出席兩會，他在機場主動回應稱校方判決很合適，批評涉事學生「目無尊長、態度囂張」，強調理大校園絕不容許有人宣傳港獨。<br />\n<br />\n劉炳章指摘學生去年擅自改動民主牆的管理守則，又「搞絕食」，最後更衝擊學校管理層。他稱翻看當日影片，見到有學生在辦公室外叫囂、逐間房拍門要求校長出來，「有少少好似黑社會『刮友』咁嘅感覺」，認為學生不單不尊重師長，更不准後來到場勸說的兩名教授離開，「我形住佢涉嫌禁錮」。<br />\n<br />\n他又自爆曾多次催促校方作出判決，又指昨日的判決「嚟得遲」，希望今次裁決令教職員和學生都知道校內絕不容許宣傳港獨，也不容許學生有如此囂張、誇張、目無尊長的行為。"},{"pid":"02e035e180208f103de252db386fb319c0d9c5f2","tid":1043246,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:17:03.000Z","msg":"出席者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%B1%E5%B0%8F%E6%A1%83%E5%9C%92%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E6%25B5%2581%25E6%25B5%25AE%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25A1%2583%25E5%259C%2592%25E9%25A3%25AF%25E5%25B1%2580&d=Xug72IqGonTeMs94ciZuWhUxn6Ez5IAhGrAWUjzTwv4%3D&h=82d4dff6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%B5%81%E6%B5%AE%E5%B1%B1%E5%B0%8F%E6%A1%83%E5%9C%92%E9%A3%AF%E5%B1%80</a><br />\n